## Current Styling Philosophy

Brand style:

* Modern
* Clean
* Minimal
* Trustworthy
* Neutral

Color direction:

* White backgrounds
* Light gray cards
* Soft borders
* Subtle shadows
* Professional ecommerce appearance

Avoid:

* Bright colors
* Overly flashy UI
* Tailwind

Use plain CSS only.

## Architectural Decisions Already Made

Products use:

/products/[slug]

instead of:

/products/[id]

Reason:

* Better SEO
* Better sharing
* Better UX

Firestore document IDs remain the primary database identifier.

Slug is only used for URLs.

Products contain:

* id
* sellerId
* slug

Orders use timeline tracking.

Products are archived instead of deleted.

Phone numbers will be collected during registration but phone verification is postponed until after business validation.

Authentication MVP:

* Email/Password
* Google Sign-In
* Forgot Password Email

No SMS verification in V1.

