## Instructions For Future Chats

Always review this entire document before making recommendations.

Prioritize:

* Simplicity
* Scalability
* Startup practicality

Do not redesign folder structure unless absolutely necessary.

Respect all architecture decisions already made.

At the beginning of every new chat:

1. Review Current Progress.
2. Identify the next logical milestone.
3. Continue from where the project stopped.
4. Avoid repeating completed work.
